revision.text:
{{Commons cat|Aftermath of World War II}}
*'''[[Aftermath of World War II]]''' — events of the direct aftermath of [[World War II]], which had ended in 1945.

{{clr}}
:::*Note: ''This category is for articles concerning [[World War II]] that deal primarily with the immediate [[Aftermath of World War II|aftermath of the war]]. Only articles eligible for [[:Category:World War II]] should be placed in this subcategory. Examples include peace treaties, war reparations, post-war diplomatic negotiations. The articles should be primarily concerned with World War II and its aftermath, and not a consequence that arose in subsequent years.''

:::{{For|consequences in subsequent years|Category: Cold War}}

[[Category:World War II]]
[[Category:Aftermath of wars|World War II]]
