==Old Content== {{Commons cat|Aftermath of World War II}} *'''[[:en:Aftermath of World War II|Aftermath of World War II]]''' — events of the direct aftermath of [[:en:Pacific War|Pacific War]], which had ended in 1945. {{clr}} ::*Note: ''This category is for articles concerning [[:en:Pacific War|Pacific War]] that deal primarily with the immediate [[:en:Aftermath of World War II|aftermath of the war]]. Only articles eligible for [[:Category:World War II]] should be placed in this subcategory. Examples include peace treaties, war reparations, post-war diplomatic negotiations. The articles should be primarily concerned with World War II and its aftermath, and not a consequence that arose in subsequent years.'' ::{{For|consequences in subsequent years|Category: Cold War}} {{draft categories|
